Mario Balotelli has been subjected to more than 4,000 racist messages on social media this season . 
  Liverpool manager Brendan Rodgers says he is 'surprised and shocked' at the level of abuse . 
  Daniel Sturridge and Arsenal striker Danny Welbeck have also been targeted . 
  Anti-discrimination body Kick It Out estimates 134,000 discriminatory posts this season  . 
  Stoke City boss Mark Hughes has called for a crackdown on racism . 
 